            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">The Collection offers a first hand account of Dorothy Krampitz Evarts experiences in Hawaii as a civil service worker during World War II. The Collection is made up of Mrs. Evarts’ interview and the subsequent video log.</abstract>
